    <lb n="25" break="no"/>τα. <unclear>δι</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/> δέ σοι χωρὶς τῶν προκειμένων κούφ<unclear>ων</unclear> <choice><reg>ὠπτημένα</reg><orig><unclear>ὀ</unclear>πτημένα</orig></choice> 

